24th July 2015 ITV4
19:00 to 20:00 Stage 19 Highlights

Stage 19 is a short but unrelenting 138km, taking the peloton over the Col de Chaussy, the Col de la Croix de Fer, and the Col du Mollard before the final climb up to La Toussuire - Les Sybelles. Presented by Gary Imlach with analysis from Chris Boardman, commentary from Phil Liggett and Paul Sherwen with Ned Boulting reporting at the roadside.
